oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Train depot in Giles County
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a train stopped at a depot near Crescent View Farm in Giles County. There are people standing by the depot building (on left) and others by the train car (center).
